<div id="deletetypeModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-[9999] flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-midnight-violet-950/40 backdrop-blur-sm hidden">
    
    <div class="relative w-full max-w-md flex flex-col bg-silver-50 dark:bg-midnight-violet-950 rounded-xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 border-b border-ash-grey-200 dark:border-midnight-violet-800 bg-white dark:bg-midnight-violet-900 shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-tag text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 text-lg"></i>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-midnight-violet-900 dark:text-silver-50">Smazat typ?</h2>
            </div>
            <button type="button" id="deletetypeClose" class="text-gray-400 dark:text-silver-500 hover:text-gray-600 dark:hover:text-silver-200 transition-colors p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-ash-grey-100 dark:hover:bg-midnight-violet-800">
                <i class="fas fa-times text-xl"></i>
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-silver-50 dark:bg-[#150f18] text-center md:text-left">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-silver-300 leading-relaxed">
                Opravdu chcete odstranit tento <span class="font-bold text-midnight-violet-900 dark:text-silver-100">typ zařízení</span>? 
                <br><br>
                Tato akce může ovlivnit zobrazení stávajících MCU, které mají tento typ přiřazen. Akce je <span class="font-bold text-red-600">nevratná</span>.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 border-t border-ash-grey-200 dark:border-midnight-violet-800 bg-white dark:bg-midnight-violet-900 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-end gap-3 shrink-0">
            <button type="button" id="deletetypeCancel" 
                class="order-2 sm:order-1 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-ash-grey-200 dark:bg-midnight-violet-800 text-ash-grey-800 dark:text-silver-200 font-medium hover:bg-ash-grey-300 dark:hover:bg-midnight-violet-700 transition-colors">
                Zrušit
            </button>
            <button type="button" id="deletetypeSubmit" 
                class="order-1 sm:order-2 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-red-600 text-white font-medium hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i>
                Potvrdit smazání
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>